{"tid":757714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮證實北韓歸還韓戰中陣亡美軍遺骸","createTime":"2018-07-27T05:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T06:22:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc2a067c8e4439e76e4e1ca02a1d687146a143f","tid":757714,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1409177_1_L_20180727105458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1409177_1_L_20180727105458.jpg&h=c9f6081b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日是兩韓簽署《韓戰停戰協定》65周年，美國白宮證實，北韓歸還在韓戰中陣亡的美軍遺骸。<br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人桑德斯表示，美軍C-17運輸機飛往北韓元山市接載遺骸，返回南韓首爾以南的烏山空軍基地。<br />\n<br />\n桑德斯又說，北韓的行動以及持續積極的改變，令到華府鼓舞。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普和北韓領袖金正恩上月在新加坡舉行峰會，並達成協議，包括北韓承諾歸還美軍遺骸。"},{"pid":"9c41ea99c658a951a9c66b027c868894bbae5edf","tid":757714,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早排唔係話金仔又搞搞陣既咩"},{"pid":"b55a4429bd1eb2b5338d1dd32eaba4a67eade6c2","tid":757714,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9c41ea99c658a951a9c66b027c868894bbae5edf","tid":757714,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早排唔係話金仔又搞搞陣既咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:33:29.000Z","msg":"主要係習總叫金仔搞搞震<br />\n<br />\n依家習總都被TRUMP打, 金仔仲唔醒水？ 仲聽條ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 維呢老點咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fdb6747c26c4812291072855de532fb0682d31","tid":757714,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:37:23.000Z","msg":"